  2006                                  ;
  2007                                  ;       Out:            N/A             This routine does not exit.
  2008                                  ;
  2009                                  ;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  2010                                  ReportInterrupt         push    ds                                              ;save DS at time of interrupt
  2011                                                          push    es                                              ;save ES at time of interrupt
  2012                                                          pushad                                                  ;save EAX,ECX,EDX,EBX,EBP,ESP,ESI,EDI
